title: Xombi
description:
A brilliant followup to the original Milestone series, Xombi. This newer miniseries published under the DC imprint, encapsulates the origin of David Kim as well as re-establishes his non-denonminational supernatural investigating God squad.

The imaginative dark art of Frazer Irving compliments John Rozum's story.

This pack is a digital rip, not a c2c scan like prior uploads
